high_descs: Turn and cross the room until you get to the stairs, turn right again and move through the kitchen to the head of the table.
Pick the cell phone up from the table.
Carry the cell phone to the other end of the table.
Place the phone in the grey bowl on the table.
Pick up the bowl with the phone in it from the table.
Move along side the kitchen table to the living room and end standing between the sofa and the coffee table.
Place the bowl with the cell phone in it on the coffee table to the left of the laptop.
anns.task_desc: Move a cell phone in a bowl to the coffee table.

high_descs: turn right and walk to the end of the stairs, then turn right again and walk over to the dining table
grab the cellphone off of the dining table
walk around to the other side of the dining table
place the cellphone in a bowl
pick up the bowl with the cellphone in it
move to the left side of the dining table and face turn to face the same direction, then walk forwards across the room to the coffee table on your left
place the bowl down on the coffee table
anns.task_desc: place a bowl with a cellphone in it down on the coffee table

high_descs: Turn right and walk around the stairs to the closest short side of the kitchen table.
Take the cell phone off the table.
Walk around the table to the other short side.
Place the cell phone in the bowl on the table.
Pick up the bowl.
Walk forward and after the couch veer left to the coffee table.
Place the bowl on the table to the left of the laptop.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a cell phone in it on a coffee table.
